 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (FIRST OPTIONAL TRIM _ 475 WORDS _ BEGINS HERE AT 575) &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   So much for the winners. Among the losers cited by the Center
for Strategic and Budgetary Assessments, another Washington
think-tank, is the whole principle of ``tactical air power'' _ the
powerful but relatively small and short-range fighters and bombers
