<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-22 10:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6325 &Cx1f; tad-z
r k BC-KELSO-COLUMN23-COX     12-22 0853
