look whether they know it or not. Nolan Miller is the man who
dressed Mary Ann in gingham for ``Gilligan's Island.'' He put Peggy
Lipton in hip huggers for ``The Mod Squad.'' And he created those
linebacker-wide shoulder pads for Krystle Carrington on
``Dynasty.'' (Sturrock, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
