recently bet on a Dolphins game. ``If they won, my friend said
she'd pay for me and another friend to spend a week at Doral
Saturnia,'' she says, referring to the swank Miami spa where
robe-clad socialites agonize over whether to schedule a Swedish
massage or shiatsu. ``If they lost, I'd do some work for her for
free.'' Well, Maribel's going to Miami. And her pal's going to be
out about six grand. Bottom line: Maribel frolics with rich folks.
Really rich folks. (Grantham, Palm Beach) MOVED.
