federal officials in encouraging Americans to celebrate this
holiday season, but to be extra cautious amid fears of related
terrorism at home and abroad. FBI counter-terrorism chief Dale
Watson says threats have been issued against the United States. By
JOHN HENRY and STEVE LASH.
</P>
