   Y2K-GLITCHES (Washington) _ Assuming the United States makes it
through New Year's weekend with few Y2K-related computer glitches,
it doesn't necessarily mean Y2K will be a non-event. In fact, most
Y2K problems likely won't reveal themselves until Monday, Jan. 3,
when millions of Americans return to work and school. By JENNIFER
CORBETT DOOREN. (Already filed.)
</P>
