been known as ``Linebacker U'' for its proud tradition of producing
stellar linebackers. But Texas A&AMP;M boasts its own legacy of
producing star linebackers, and the Aggies intend to show the
Nittany Lions which school is really ``Linebacker U'' in next
week's Alamo Bowl. By NEIL HOHLFELD.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-OU-CINCY (Norman, Okla.) _ Oklahoma plays host to No.
4-ranked Cincinnati in a nationally televised non-conference
college basketball matchup. By JEROME SOLOMON.
</P>
