Diego Padres sent second baseman-leadoff hitter Quilvio Veras,
first baseman Wally Joyner and left fielder Reggie Sanders to the
Atlanta Braves today in exchange for first baseman Ryan Klesko,
second baseman Bret Boone and minor league pitcher Jason Shiel.
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
