<P>
   BBN -ROCKER-MAIN _ ATLANTA _ Braves pitcher John Rocker makes
derogatory comments about homosexuals, foreigners, single mothers
and only Sports Illustrated knows what else. In the magazine's next
issue, Rocker lists all of the above as reasons why he would retire
from baseball before he would ever play in New York. (Stinson,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 16.
