government, locally produced Web sites and chat rooms have
proliferated rapidly here in the last two years, giving Chinese a
forum for public debate and discussion _ even a degree of dissent _
that was previously unavailable. By Elisabeth Rosenthal.
</P>
<P>
   (See also CHINA-ONLINE-BIZ, a financial story.)
</P>
<P>
