   &QL; 
GAY (Washington) - Last week, Arizona Sen. John McCain collected
$40,000 from a fund-raiser sponsored by the Log Cabin Republicans,
a gay GOP group. But, in the same week, the ``Washington Blade''
called McCain an ``enigma,'' on gay issues, noting he was once
