<P>
   MANNESMANN-MARKETPLACE (London) _ The battleground for the
Vodafone Airtouch-Mannesmann struggle is Europe, but America is the
basic source of the investment bankers and the tactics. Wednesday,
America also became the source of the first shareholder proxy fight
in the biggest corporate takeover brawl of all time. Upset by the
refusal of Mannesmann's board to negotiate with its hostile suitor,
a prominent American investor in the German telecommunications
conglomerate said he would wage a campaign to oust the company's
